01 — Brand Identity

Who We Are

Genius Eco Visionaries is a recycling company based in Edo State, Nigeria that operates its own recycling plant. We buy plastics and aluminium cans from households, businesses, and institutions, then process them into recycled raw materials sold as feedstock to manufacturers — completing the circular economy loop while turning everyday waste into income for our community.

01
Mission
Sustainable waste management through recycling — collecting materials from the community, processing them at our plant into reusable feedstock, and supplying manufacturers. A circular economy that turns waste into value.
02
Vision
To become the leading force in recycling and environmental innovation across Nigeria — starting from Edo South and expanding into Edo North, Central, and beyond.
03
Values
Sustainability · Innovation · Community Impact · Integrity · Excellence · Environmental Responsibility — these six values guide every decision we make.

02 — Logo

Logo System

The logo features two leaves with open hands in a circular yin-yang motif — representing recycling, sustainability, and community partnership. The hands symbolise giving and receiving, central to our buy-back model.

09 — Voice & Tone Guidelines

How We Speak

GEV communicates warmth, empowerment, and simplicity. We lead with the benefit to the customer — always.

✓ Public Website Voice
  • "Turn your waste into cash" — lead with the customer benefit
  • "We come to you" — emphasise free, convenient pickup
  • "We pay you" — clear, direct value proposition
  • Warm, community-first, eco-conscious language
  • Always Naira (₦) with per-kg unit for pricing
  • "Small changes, big impact" — connect personal action to environment
✓ Admin Dashboard Voice
  • Concise, action-oriented labels ("Assign Driver" not "Click here to...")
  • Data-driven language — weights, amounts, counts
  • Clear confirmation after every action
  • Error messages explain what to do, not what went wrong
  • Neutral, professional — no exclamation marks in admin
✓ Colour Usage
  • Blue-500 for navigation, links, and interactive elements
  • Green-400 for CTAs related to money and eco actions
  • Neutral grays for body text and borders
  • Light tints (50/100) as section backgrounds
  • WCAG AA contrast ratios (4.5:1 minimum)
✗ Don'ts
  • Don't use Blue and Green as equal-weight CTAs on the same view
  • Don't use red for non-error purposes
  • Don't introduce new brand colours outside this palette
  • Don't mix font families within the same element
  • Don't go below 12px for any text
  • Don't use ALL CAPS for body text (only labels)

10 — Implementation

Tailwind CSS Config

Copy into tailwind.config.js to make all design tokens available as Tailwind utility classes in the Rails app.

// tailwind.config.js const defaultTheme = require("tailwindcss/defaultTheme") module.exports = { content: [ "./app/views/**/*.{html,erb}", "./app/javascript/**/*.js", "./app/helpers/**/*.rb", ], theme: { extend: { colors: { blue: { 50: "#E8F4F8", 100: "#C5E4EE", 200: "#8DC9DD", 300: "#55AECC", 400: "#35A4C8", 500: "#28A0C8", 600: "#2290B5", 700: "#1B7A99", 800: "#15647D", 900: "#0E4457", }, green: { 50: "#F0F7E6", 100: "#D9EDBE", 200: "#BCE293", 300: "#A0D768", 400: "#8CC83C", 500: "#7DB835", 600: "#6FA52F", 700: "#5C8D27", 800: "#49751F", 900: "#365413", }, gray: { 50: "#F7FAFA", 100: "#EEF2F3", 200: "#DCE1E3", 300: "#B8C0C4", 400: "#8B969C", 500: "#657078", 600: "#4A545B", 700: "#353D42", 800: "#232A2E", 900: "#141919", }, success: { DEFAULT: "#2ECC71", light: "#E8F8F0" }, warning: { DEFAULT: "#F39C12", light: "#FEF5E7" }, error: { DEFAULT: "#E74C3C", light: "#FDEDEC" }, }, fontFamily: { display: ["Plus Jakarta Sans", ...defaultTheme.fontFamily.sans], body: ["DM Sans", ...defaultTheme.fontFamily.sans], mono: ["JetBrains Mono", ...defaultTheme.fontFamily.mono], }, borderRadius: { sm: "6px", md: "10px", lg: "16px", xl: "24px", }, boxShadow: { xs: "0 1px 2px rgba(20,25,25,.05)", sm: "0 1px 3px rgba(20,25,25,.08), 0 1px 2px rgba(20,25,25,.04)", md: "0 4px 6px -1px rgba(20,25,25,.08), 0 2px 4px -2px rgba(20,25,25,.04)", lg: "0 10px 15px -3px rgba(20,25,25,.08), 0 4px 6px -4px rgba(20,25,25,.04)", xl: "0 20px 25px -5px rgba(20,25,25,.08), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(20,25,25,.04)", }, }, }, plugins: [ require("@tailwindcss/forms"), require("@tailwindcss/typography"), ], }
/* app/assets/stylesheets/application.tailwind.css */ @tailwind base; @tailwind components; @tailwind utilities; @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap'); @layer base { body { @apply font-body text-gray-800 antialiased; } h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 { @apply font-display; } }
